Painting Before Moving In: Pros & Cons
‚úÖ Pros
Easier and Faster ProcessWith an empty home, there‚Äôs no need to move furniture, cover belongings, or worry about getting paint on your brand-new couch. Painters (or you) can move freely, making the whole process faster.
